@startuml
title Componentes de Arquitetura — Sistema Academia SA
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "Frontend" {
  [React/Vite] as Frontend
  [AuthContext] as AuthContext
  [Api.js / Axios] as Axios
}

package "Backend Node.js + Express" {
  [API Express] as API
  [Middlewares\nAuth / Escopo / Permissão] as Middlewares
  [Services] as Services
  [Auth] as Auth
  [Auditoria] as Auditoria
  [Financeiro] as Financeiro
  [Acessos] as Acessos
  [Uploads] as Uploads
}

database "SQLite atual" as SQLite
database "PostgreSQL futuro" as PostgreSQL
cloud "Uploads/Storage futuro" as Storage
cloud "Backup futuro" as Backup
node "Integração futura\ncatraca/câmera" as Catraca

Frontend --> AuthContext
AuthContext --> Axios
Axios --> API : HTTP/JSON\nBearer atual\nCookie refresh futuro no frontend
API --> Middlewares
Middlewares --> Services
Services --> Auth
Services --> Auditoria
Services --> Financeiro
Services --> Acessos
Services --> Uploads

Auth --> SQLite
Auditoria --> SQLite
Financeiro --> SQLite
Acessos --> SQLite
Uploads --> SQLite

SQLite ..> PostgreSQL : migração futura
Uploads ..> Storage : futuro
SQLite ..> Backup : futuro
Catraca ..> API : integração futura

note right of Auth
Sessão opaca server-side.
Refresh token em cookie HttpOnly no backend.
Sem JWT.
end note

note bottom of Auditoria
Auditoria é mecanismo técnico.
Histórico de Atividades é o módulo visual
somente leitura.
end note
@enduml
